────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
THIRD-PARTY DATASET NOTICES
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

This repository contains ONLY source code (CUDA/C++/Python scripts).
No dataset files are included or distributed.

The dataset preparation scripts reference the following third-party datasets,
each governed by its own separate license:

1. Oxford 17-Category Flower Dataset
   Authors : Nilsback & Zisserman (CVPR 2006)
   License : Research / non-commercial use only — see Oxford VGG terms
   URL     : https://www.robots.ox.ac.uk/~vgg/data/flowers/17/

2. PASCAL Visual Object Classes (VOC) 2007
   Authors : Everingham et al. (IJCV 2010)
   License : Research / non-commercial use — see PASCAL VOC terms
   URL     : http://host.robots.ox.ac.uk/pascal/VOC/

3. Oxford-IIIT Pet Dataset
   Authors : Parkhi et al. (CVPR 2012)
   License : Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 (CC-BY-SA 4.0)
   URL     : https://www.robots.ox.ac.uk/~vgg/data/pets/

Users must download these datasets independently and comply with each
dataset's own terms before use.

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
THIRD-PARTY MODEL / ALGORITHM NOTICES
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

This project implements algorithms described in academic papers. The
following papers are cited for attribution; their methods are reproduced
in original CUDA code under the MIT License above:

  • Batch Normalization    — Ioffe & Szegedy, ICML 2015
  • He (Kaiming) Init      — He et al., ICCV 2015
  • Momentum SGD           — Sutskever et al., ICML 2013
  • cuDNN Primitives       — Chetlur et al., 2014
  • Dropout                — Srivastava et al., JMLR 2014
  • AlexNet architecture   — Krizhevsky et al., NeurIPS 2012
  • VGGNet architecture    — Simonyan & Zisserman, ICLR 2015
  • ResNet                 — He et al., CVPR 2016
  • Feature Pyramid Networks — Lin et al., CVPR 2017
  • RetinaNet / Focal Loss — Lin et al., ICCV 2017
  • U-Net                  — Ronneberger et al., MICCAI 2015
  • Attention U-Net        — Oktay et al., MIDL 2018
  • DeepLab v3+            — Chen et al., ECCV 2018
  • Dilated Convolutions   — Yu & Koltun, ICLR 2016
  • Dice Loss / V-Net      — Milletari et al., 3DV 2016
  • Cutout                 — DeVries & Taylor, 2017
  • Elastic Deformation    — Simard et al., ICDAR 2003

All implementations are original CUDA/C++ code written from scratch.
No pre-trained weights, model binaries, or third-party code are included.
